## 2026-04-08 - Import source selection gives too many equal-weight choices at once and mixes very different source families
- Reworked the import chooser into a progressive disclosure flow: users now pick a source family first (`From Figma`, `From token files`, `From code`, `Migrate from another tool`) and only then see the specific import formats in that family, with family-relevant guidance shown in context instead of as global caveats.
- Kept all existing import handlers and hidden file inputs intact, preserved drag-and-drop auto-detection, and tightened the drag overlay copy so file-based imports still feel available outside the family picker.
- Files changed: `packages/figma-plugin/src/ui/components/ImportSourceSelector.tsx` ~L4, ~L20, ~L64, ~L101, ~L298; `packages/figma-plugin/src/ui/components/ImportPanel.tsx` ~L77

